[SHORT DESC]
Puts the foe to sleep.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Puts the target to sleep.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/sleep_powder">Sleep Powder</a> is a Grass-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/hypnosis">Hypnosis</a> is a Psychic-type equivalent, but with 15% less accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/sing">Sing</a> is an equivalent move, but with 20% less accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/grasswhistle">GrassWhistle</a> is a Grass-type equivalent, but with 20% less accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/spore">Spore</a> is a Grass-type equivalent, but with 25% more accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/yawn">Yawn</a> is an equivalent move, but puts the target to sleep at the end of the second turn.</p>